Build and run instructions

1) Make sure you have the latest linux-headers and build-essential
1a) sudo apt-get install <whatever you don't have>

2) cd to wherever you unzipped the Project 4 folder.

3) make

4) cd modules

5) sudo insmod upperReverse.ko buffer_size=<however big you want>

Optional
----------------------------

6) lsmod (check the very top to make sure it's in the kernel)

7) ls -l /dev/upperReverse (checks that the device driver was made)

-----------------------------

8) sudo ./test '<any string>'
